(69, 'XPERTIZE', 'Intérim, recrutement', 'le site internet: https://www.xpertize.africa/Description de l entreprise Installé au Maroc et au Sénégal, Xpertize Africa est un acteur international dans le domaine des Ressources Humaines qui accompagne de nombreuses entreprises sur l’ensemble du continent africain. Initié en 2012, le cabinet a notamment créé le 1er portail de cooptation du pays et compte près de 60 collaborateurs. En 2018, Xpertize Africa est devenu partenaire du Groupe Select, expert international des solutions RH depuis 1987, implanté en Belgique, au Luxembourg, aux Pays-Bas et aux Émirats arabes unis, à travers une vingtaine d’agences. Notre expertise : Recrutement / Executive Search / Project Sourcing / Conseil RH. Nos secteurs : Engineering / ICT / Sales, Marketing & Office / Ressources Humaines / Finance, Banque et Assurance. Based in Morocco and Senegal, Xpertize Africa is an international player in the field of Human Resources and supports many companies across the African continent. Created in 2012, the firm has created the first co-optation portal in Morocco and has nearly 60 employees. In 2018, Xpertize Africa became a part of Select Group, an international expert in HR solutions since 1987, established in Belgium, Luxembourg, the Netherlands and the United Arab Emirates, through twenty agencies. Our services : Recruitment / Executive Search / Project Sourcing / HR Consultancy. Our sectors : Engineering / ICT / Sales, Marketing & Office / Human Resources / Finance, Banking and Insurance.'),
