(666, '', 'Informatique / Electronique - Multimédia / Internet - Secteur Informatique', 'le site internet: Description de l entrepriseEntreprise : DXC is the world’s leading independent, end-to-end IT services company, helping clients harness the power of innovation to thrive on change. Created by the merger of CSC and the Enterprise Services business of Hewlett Packard Enterprise, DXC Technology is a $25 billion company with a 60-year legacy of delivering results for thousands of clients in more than 70 countries. With over 11 years of IT Services expertise and 1200 employees, DXC in Morocco is a Joint venture between DXC Technology and CDG Group. Our Service Center accompanies the largest institutions in the Moroccan and global markets. DXC in Morocco is based on 2 Sites : Technopolis, & Casablanca Nearshore. Our company offers a wide portfolio of end-to-end services enabling digital transformation: Datacenter, Cloud ITO, Applications, Analytics, Workplace, Business Process and Security.'),
