(103, ' Senior DevOps Cloud Engineer AWS / Azure / GCP English Speaking', 'CDI', 'Expérience entre 2 ans et 5 ans', 3, 'Job Role: Work with Cloud developers, product managers and designers to guide and make technical decisions throughout the development process. Mentor other developers and contractors throughout the development lifecycle. Prototype unproven concepts to inform final implementations. Stay abreast of cloud trends and topics. Automate everything possible. Leverages CI/CD to automate repeatable tasks and quality checks. Managing Infrastructure as Code. Building the tools and support for teams to be able to self-manage in an owner operator model   Employment Terms: Job: Full Time Location: Casablanca - Settat Region / Rabat/ Salé Region / Remote. Contract: Permanent Contract (CDI) Salary: to be discussed in line with experience and qualifications  Benefits: Access to a Fitness Club Telephone Contract Professional onboarding Process & Experience with European Team Free Access to E-learning Platform A Professional environment and a team with Casual & friendly character Progressive salary with fast learning & adaptation pace A Corporate Mobile computer Professional Event & Team building events Possibility to work Remotely Complementary health insurance (ongoing) Incentives After a successful evaluation period of 1 - 2 years, the European blue card can be requested by changing the job location to Germany', 103);
