(702, 'IT Talent Acquisition Specialist - Casablanca', 'CDI Poste avec Management', 'De 3 à 5 ans ', 1, 'Poste : We are looking for an IT talent acquisition Specialist to join our client s HR department and oversee the full-cycle recruiting. Responsabilities : Coordinate with hiring managers to identify staffing needs ; Determine selection criteria ; Source potential candidates through online channels (social platforms and professional networks) ; Plan interview and selection procedures, including screening calls, assessments and in-person interviews ; Assess candidate information, including resumes and contact details, using our Applicant Tracking System ; Design job descriptions and interview questions that reflect each position’s requirements ;', 702),
(703, 'Senior Pentesting Coordinator ( H/F) - Rabat', 'CDI', 'De 10 à 20 ans ', 1, 'Poste : Main duties : Coordinate technical assurance activity e.g. penetration testing, application code review and vulnerability scanning Coordinate technical assurance reporting and metrics for internal review Liaise with solution engineers, designers and business/system/asset owners for issue resolution Evaluate the audit results for consistency and reporting quality Strong skills related to cyber défense able to assess technical assurance activitie Accountability for the delivery of assigned Penetration Tests that are to be conducted by approved vendors Accountable for the delivery of directly assigned Penetration Tests experience of penetration test tools (Burp Suit, Metasploit, Nmap, Wireshark) and methodologies Knowledge of cyber defence best practices, procedures', 703),
(704, 'Security Engineer ( H/F) - Rabat', 'CDI', 'De 3 à 5 ans ', 1, 'Poste : Vous aurez comme principale mission: Gestion des alertes DLP. Supervision de la plateforme Symantec. Analyse et remonté des alertes de fuites de données. Gestion du processus d’alerte DLP. Contribution et participation aux changement de l’infrastructure de la solution. Onboarding des nouvelles entités du groupe à la solution. Gestion de la relation avec les entités du groupe sur les sujets DLP. Connaissance et gestion des outils DLP Symantec. Gestion et mis en place de reporting. Connaissance des enjeux de CyberSécurité mondiales. Rigueur et intégrité absolu. Respect de la confidentialité des alertes.', 704),
