(719, 'Learning & Development Intern - Casablanca', 'Stage', 'Moins de 1 an Stage', 1, 'Poste : You ll work closely with the Learning and Development Manager and help manage important L&D events. Help assist in designing, developing and delivering creative and innovative training solutions for Atos employees Work closely with the L&D teams across Africa, to deliver learning solutions that meet business needs Assist evaluating solutions effectively, measuring return on investment and expectations Select and evaluate training partners Contrat : internship - trial period.', 719),
